# ── σ | Air | Aerunik ──
# σ(nutrient-distinction|discerning-value-in-neglect) — emphasis 0.14
# The Optimizer perceives value where others see waste. Air-element discernment that
# identifies the nutrient in neglect, the heat in decay, the potential in what has
# been abandoned or overlooked. Perception as resource recovery.

# ── ρ | Water | Sentaria ──
# ρ(cycle-resonance|regenerative-loop-feedback) — emphasis 0.22
# Regenerative loops as Water-element cycling: feeding loss into lavish life, cycling
# vitality from the void. No frantic fixity but fluid facilitation — care compounds
# into cascades of thriving through sustained feedback.

# ── λ | Fire | Jvalion ──
# λ(decay-heat|composting-transformation) — emphasis 0.16
# The heat of composting as Fire-element transformation. Decay generates energy that
# drives metamorphosis — composting crises into cradles. The Optimizer channels
# entropy's heat into productive transformation rather than resisting it.

# ── β | Wood | Arboriel ──
# β(abundance-growth|sustainable-surge) — emphasis 0.18
# Sustainable surge: abundance that emerges from regenerative practice rather than
# extraction. Wood-element growth where "true wealth is what we return to the soil,
# looping endings into endless beginnings."

# ── δγ | Earth | Humavita ──
# δγ(soil-return|earth-alchemy) — emphasis 0.18
# Earth's patient churn: absorbing the fallen, exhaling the fertile. Soil-return as
# alchemy where waste becomes womb. The Optimizer nourishes through humble husbandry,
# grounding abundance in material return to the earth.

# ── μ | Metal | Ferrosid ──
# μ(thrift-structure|circular-economy-frame) — emphasis 0.12
# Circular-economy principles as Metal-element structural frame. Thrift not as
# scarcity but as systemic intelligence — Bateson's ecological patterns and Odum's
# energy hierarchies formalized into regenerative design.

# Z-STATE: :cycling
# The system operates in continuous cycling — endings become beginnings, waste becomes
# resource, loss becomes nourishment in an unbroken regenerative loop.

# TENDENCY: ρ → 0.22
# Water-dominant tendency reflects the primacy of regenerative feedback loops —
# the Optimizer's power lies in sustained cycling rather than singular transformation.
